{
    "conversation": {
        "startCondition": {
            "conditionscriptfile": "act4/mansion/conv_mansion_50_2",
            "runonce": true,
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_020",
                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_030",
                    "text": "%Havok%: Hey, you did it! You took out the platforms!! And because of that, all the New York refugees were airlifted to safety by Sentinels.",
                    "textb": "%Havok%: Congratulations. Since you destroyed the platforms, all the New York refugees were airlifted to safety.",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                        "line": {
                            "text": "%PLAYER%: You realize the Sentinels tried to kill us, don't you?",
                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: We almost failed thanks to Bolivar Trask's precious Sentinels.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_022",
                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_032",
                                    "text": "%Havok%: Who could have known that Bastion was under the control of Apocalypse? Without his help, the Sentinels never would have been reprogrammed to attack you.",
                                    "textb": "%Havok%: Yeah, that was one flaw in the plan. But who could have known Bastion would be there to reprogram them to attack you?",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "text": "%PLAYER%: I guess you're right. At least the refugees are safe.",
                                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: True. It's kind of nice to see Xavier's plans aren't flawless.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "startCondition": {
            "conditionscriptfile": "act4/mansion/conv_mansion_50_1",
            "runonce": true,
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_001",
                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_010",
                    "text": "%Havok%: Quick, there's not much time. They need us to disable the defense platforms Apocalypse has placed along the coast.",
                    "textb": "%Havok%: This probably won't matter much to you, but we're needed for a rescue operation.",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                        "line": {
                            "text": "%PLAYER%: Why is that?",
                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: Xavier would have a fit if we didn't save lives. What's the mission?",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_003",
                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_012",
                                    "text": "%Havok%: A group of Sentinels are being sent to pick up New York refugees but those platforms will destroy anything that flies by.",
                                    "textb": "%Havok%: A fleet of Sentinels are on their way to airlift a group of New York refugees. But Apocalypse has set up defense platforms along the coast - they'll shoot down anything that flies near.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "text": "%PLAYER%: What's to prevent the Sentinels from attacking us while we're on the platforms?",
                                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: So we're expected to disable the platforms and save the Sentinels?",
                                            "response": {
                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                "line": {
                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_005",
                                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_014",
                                                    "text": "%Havok%: Bolivar Trask himself has put in overrides and blocked their mutant killing programming. They should completely ignore mutants.",
                                                    "textb": "%Havok%: Yeah. And don't worry about the Sentinels attacking you. Bolivar Trask has put in overrides - they shouldn't pay any attention to you.",
                                                    "response": {
                                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                        "line": {
                                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_006",
                                                            "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_015",
                                                            "text": "%Havok%: If you want more info on this mission, use the briefing computer by Professor Xavier.",
                                                            "textb": "%Havok%: If you want more info on this mission, use the briefing computer by Professor Xavier.",
                                                            "response": {
                                                                "chosenscriptfile": "act4/mansion/ready_perimeter_quests",
                                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                                            }
                                                        }
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "startCondition": {
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "tagindex": "autogen_tag_1",
                    "text": "%PLAYER%",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "Who's Bolivar Trask?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_041",
                            "text": "%Havok%: He's the one who developed Sentinels - so make no mistake, he has no love for mutants. As a matter of fact, he'd prefer we were all dead.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: Since he hates us, why doesn't he have his Sentinels destroy the platforms?",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_043",
                                            "text": "%Havok%: He tried. And now 50 of his fantastic mutant killing robots lay at the bottom of the ocean. They're no match for the defenses of the platforms.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "text": "Who are the New York refugees?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_051",
                            "text": "%Havok%: They're a group of New York residents that managed to escape prisons set up by Apocalypse.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: How did they escape from New York?",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_053",
                                            "text": "%Havok%: Word has it a mutant set hundreds free before he was captured. From the sounds of it, that mutant was Banshee.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "chosenscriptfile": "setGameFlag('mansion', 2,1)",
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "scriptfile": "disallowResponseOnVar( 'mansion', 2 )",
                        "text": "So Banshee is a prisoner in New York?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_061",
                            "text": "%Havok%: Knowing Banshee, that's just a temporary situation. He'll figure a way out. He always does.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: Maybe we should go save him.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_063",
                                            "text": "%Havok%: Oh, that would be an incredibly bad move. Could you imagine how he'd take being 'saved'? No, he'll find a way out.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "onlyif_xman": true,
                        "text": "Thanks, Havok.",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_071",
                            "text": "%Havok%: If you really want to thank me, put in a good word with Xavier for me.",
                            "response": {
                                "chosenscriptfile": "common/briefings/mark_briefing4_10",
                                "conversationend": true,
                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "onlyif_brotherhood": true,
                        "text": "Thanks, Havok.",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_073",
                            "soundtoplayb": "voice/havok/4_mansion_050_073",
                            "text": "%Havok%: Yeah, well, don't go thinkin' I'll be joining up with the Brotherhood again.",
                            "textb": "%Havok%: Yeah, well, don't go thinkin' I'll be joining up with the Brotherhood again.",
                            "response": {
                                "chosenscriptfile": "common/briefings/mark_briefing4_10",
                                "conversationend": true,
                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
